      <h1 class='title'>Social Fund Commissioner</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 01 December 2003 vol 415 c47WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_47ws' title='Col. 47WS &mdash; HC Deb 01 December 2003 vol 415 c47WS' name='column_47ws' href='#column_47ws' rel='bookmark'>47WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0415P2_20031201_CWS_6'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-smith' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0415P2_20031201_CWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Smith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-smith" title="Mr Andrew Smith">The Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Andrew Smith)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I am pleased to announce that Sir Richard Tilt has agreed to serve as Social Fund Commissioner for Great Britain and Northern Ireland for a further period of three years from 1 December 2003.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
